'''Corellian Vehicle Reclamation''' was [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia's]] leading [[Landspeeder/Legends|landspeeder]] repossession company. It was repeatedly attacked by local gangs that were hired by enraged customers whose vehicles had been repossessed.

The company's CEO often hired armed individuals to eliminate those gangs to prevent further attacks.

==Behind the scenes==
This company is mentioned in the mission "Stop Rampages Through My Officer" that is available at Mission Terminals on Corellia in [[Star Wars Galaxies|''Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided'']]. The CEO hires the player to attack the base of a gang and destroy it.

